# EF Core migration scaffolding is auto-generated: GitHub collapses these files in
# PR diffs and excludes them from diff stats, so reviews show only hand-written code.
# The hand-written migration itself (<timestamp>_<Name>.cs) stays fully visible.
**/Persistence/Migrations/*.Designer.cs linguist-generated=true
**/Persistence/Migrations/*ModelSnapshot.cs linguist-generated=true
